{"tid":2437491,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梅根稱被噤聲感到寂寞　指女王對自己很好","createTime":"2021-03-08T02:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T03:04:55.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"81b866ccf64598e76a4a4ea0a4cf0d5f626fa9b9","tid":2437491,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:04:01.000Z","msg":"梅根稱被噤聲感到寂寞　指女王對自己很好<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1579321_1_20210308100051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1579321_1_20210308100051.jpg&h=b1e05243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國哈里王子與妻子梅根接受美國名嘴奧花雲費的專訪，在美國電視台播放，梅根透露，自己被噤聲，她和哈里約會公開後，身邊的人都被給予非常明確的指示，不就事件發表評論。梅根說，最初以為自己是受到保護，但是結婚後情況很快惡化，聲稱王室願意說謊來保護其他家庭成員。梅根說，結婚後有王室成員要求她在一段時間內保持低調，但梅根說幾個月沒有外出，見不到朋友感覺很寂寞。她又表示，女王伊利沙伯二世對自己一直很好。被傳與大嫂凱特關係欠佳的梅根說，英國傳媒指她惹哭凱特，反指是凱特惹哭自己。<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-08 09:58:55"},{"pid":"10438b956ead50028db1c69edc55768b11898c6b","tid":2437491,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:04:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579321-20210308.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579321-20210308.htm&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058ilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=de030c34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579321-20210308.htm&h=0fc507ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579321-20210308.htm</a>"},{"pid":"efcc8f8bdadf1ef3bfe536222c89080231d235ca","tid":2437491,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:28:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><p class=\"center\">雞</p></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cc1a4a451cca5867b9daf7c0bbfd1e998a72b8a3","tid":2437491,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:29:28.000Z","msg":"「很好」"},{"pid":"89c091e44d330ee846e0fbcfa5f8160ffddfe95e","tid":2437491,"uid":186431,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:29:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">黑雞</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adaf56145449640cce7f005a21a57005f42468b","tid":2437491,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:30:45.000Z","msg":"聲稱王室願意說謊來保護其他家庭成員。<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒指她惹哭凱特，反指是凱特惹哭自己。"},{"pid":"3dce1a52be02c2170f166889249cf4752d7ed321","tid":2437491,"uid":55598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:39:58.000Z","msg":"煩撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c746aaf4d11301a3084ca8f035447cf08365c9d","tid":2437491,"uid":318612,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"普遍上啲人唔鐘意佢並唔係因為種族。而係佢明知嫁入皇室一定有好多規矩，佢明知自己冇可能受束縛，但死都要嫁入去。一心淨係想要個title同啲錢，仲搞到自己老公同全個家族反曬面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一邊箱又話想低調做人，另一邊箱就上電視節目，扮弱者扮慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比著邊個都憎佢啦。"},{"pid":"90bfb38b42ac14f63588d94c82cf3eedfb639345","tid":2437491,"uid":66898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:50:36.000Z","msg":"唔想知 唔好講我知 出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebad31d214391c09222880d74dc1815f00db266","tid":2437491,"uid":283741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:56:46.000Z","msg":"死黑閪低撚等人種"},{"pid":"360d5688d93c8fa338e902d8a565b3706b9749b0","tid":2437491,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦臭雞  屌佢老味一撚日到黑就靠皇室個名呃飯食"},{"pid":"5d9eefe00b7630b9ad8b4614298c607d4899bb89","tid":2437491,"uid":37240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T03:04:55.000Z","msg":"呢條八婆次次見親佢都掛撚住皇室個名<br />\n明明自己大大聲講退出"}]}